data.description: Welcome Home! The intelligent layout, ideal neighborhood, and included appliances are just a few of aspects of this home you are going to love.  When you come walk through be sure to notice the large pantry, exterior cameras (for added security), and super cool digital lock system you manage with an app. Not to mention the lighting system in the trayed ceiling in the family room which offers a variety of accent colors so you can create the perfect ambiance.Close to schools, shopping, parks and more.Call to arrange your private tour. We look forward to your visit!
